		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">dodgi wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I have bought all i need to make a repro. But i still have some questions?</div>
<br />We at NESdev don't support people making repros, first it's illegal and who tell us you're not a dirty guy asking for advice from us (we freely give our free time) only to to sell them and get money ? I've been bet by a few guys this way MANY TIMES before (sivak, ...) but won't fall in again. We only support people making dev-carts for programming purpose.
<br />
<br />I hope I made myself clear.
<br />
<br />If all you wanted is just play those games play them emulated.

		

