		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We're not repro friendly because of the "dine and dash" that happened often recently.  I will answer a few of the question but I will not go more far than that.
<br />
<br />1.  Yes you can. You have to copy the same rom over and over until the end of the EPROM.
<br />
<br />2. I saw someone on the net made a megadrive cart but I'm not aware of repro. We're a nes forum after all so you won't find that information here.
<br />
<br />3. No idea what you're talking about.
<br />
<br />4. I don't have knowlege about snes board. Maybe possible but that just a guess from what I read.
<br />
<br />5. Bregalad was nice to answer this one. Only that rare japanese game can do it. It's not worth it.

		

		</td>
